author: PomplamooseMusic
description:
Perhaps my favorite song on the record…”Valse d’antan.” A collaboration with the incomparable Larry Goldings. Can’t wait to play this one in Paris in November :) 

Stream Photogénique: https://ffm.to/photogenique
Get Photogénique merch: https://photogenique.diggers.store/

Follow us on instagram: https://instagram.com/pomplamoosemusic
Become a patron of our music: http://www.patreon.com/pomplamoose

"Valse d’antan" is an original song by Pomplamoose and Larry Goldings off their album Photogénique, available now.
